lead_paragraph: Formula One teams have agreed a compromise to switch next year's first in-season test from Barcelona to Bahrain following a failed attempt to move winter testing to the warmer climes of the Middle East.

headline.print_headline: Motor Racing: F1 Teams to Switch 2017 In-Season Test to Bahrain
